channel.title: Alpha Man Project
channel.description: The Alpha Man Project podcast is about engineering the ultimate man. Alpha men are built -- not born. The host Ted Ryce overcame tragedy through health, fitness and personal development. Instead of blaming his past, he decide to inspire and educate men to take charge, step up and become the real man you were born to be. He will be interviewing top-experts in the key areas of health, wealth, relationships and personal development. As a fitness professional, Ted has helped hundreds of people get in better shape including celebrities like Richard Branson and Robert Downey Jr, CEOs of fortune 500 companies, and men who just want to look better in their bathing suits. Welcome to Alpha Man Project, the podcast that will help you to achieve greatness and be the Alpha Man. Strong. Confident. Powerful.
channel.itunes:author: Fitness & Nutrition I Dating I Career I Personal Development
channel.itunes:summary: Man up! Real men aren't born. They're built. The Alpha Man Project Podcast is about building you into the best, most badass version of yourself. Learn how to get in the best shape of your life and how to eat to build muscle and burn fat. Learn how to attract the right women and how to hold on to your balls in a relationship. Learn how to make more money to afford to live life like you envision. Education on health, fitness, nutrition, relationships, business, self-help and more. Join Ted Ryce every Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday as he inspires you to live life on your own terms. It's time for greatness. It's time to become the Alpha Man.
channel.itunes:subtitle: Man up! Become the best version of yourself.
